    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300732</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_050_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いないね……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>She's not here...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300812</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_050_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>もう、ここにはいねーのかな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah, I don't think
she's around here...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300880</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_050_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルールルー……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kuruuururu...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300956</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_050_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ここにいなきゃ、どこに？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If she's not around here,
where could she be?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301124</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_050_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わたしたち、いつも
エトと一緒だったんだよね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's so weird to be apart.
She's always been with us.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301212</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_050_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ノームの洞窟ん時以外は
ずっとな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>There was that one time
in Gnome's cavern, but...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301296</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_050_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>その前からずっと
一緒だった……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We've always been together...
all three of us...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301404</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_050_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>やっぱいつまでも
一緒にいられるって
わけと違うのかな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah, when I try to think about
it...there are no other times we've
been without Eto...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301484</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_050_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ノルンが言ってたみたいに？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But, we did our best the last
time with Gnome, remember?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301588</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_050_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……でも、オレら、
ひとりじゃ何もできないよな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah...but I don't think we
can do much alone...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301696</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_050_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……でも……できるように
ならなきゃいけないのかも……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But...if we can't do anything,
what do we do...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301764</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_050_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ダメだった……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's useless...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301852</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_050_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そんなメチャクチャに
壊れてんのか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's broken beyond repair?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301956</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_050_015&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>じゃなくて、電力不足だって。
『オズ』がそう言ってた</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No, it's not that. according to Oz,
it's lacking some electrical power.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302016</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_050_016&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>電力？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Electricity?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302108</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_050_017&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そ……うーん、
どうすりゃいいかな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah... what a bummer. Wonder
where we can find some...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302308</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_050_018&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……電気の精霊、
ヴォルトの力を借りましょう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We could ask for help from the
Summon Spirit of Electricity, Volt.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302308</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_050_019&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>かつて、ダオスと戦った時、
&lt;Cless&gt;さんは空を飛ぶ機械の力を
ヴォルトから借りたと聞きます</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Back when we were fighting Dhaos,
&lt;Cless&gt; and his party used Volt's
electricity to power up flying machines.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302440</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_050_020&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ヴォルト……か……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Volt...mmm...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302440</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_050_021&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>行ってみるか。
その精霊さん、どこにいんの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We could give it a shot!
Where is Mister Summon
Spirit right now?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302556</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_050_022&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ユークリッド大陸の南にある
&lt;Red&gt;ムジョルニア洞窟&lt;White&gt;にいたはずです</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Mjolnir cave is south of
the &lt;Red&gt;Kingdom of Euclid&lt;White&gt;.
Volt resides there.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302648</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_050_023&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>よし！　&lt;Dio&gt;くんたちも
一緒に行こうぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's settled then! &lt;Dio&gt;
and &lt;Mel&gt;, let's go!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>22</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302716</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_050_024&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でもエトが……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>B-But, we still haven't found...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>23</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302884</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_050_025&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ここにはエトちゃん、
いなかったんでしょ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Miss Eto isn't around here, right?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>24</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302884</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_050_026&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>元の時代に戻る準備できてた方が
エトちゃん喜ぶと思うよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I think Eto would be happy if the
machine was already up and kicking
by the time we find her.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>24</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302948</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_050_027&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルール！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kuruuru!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>26</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303016</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_050_028&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……わかりました</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...You've got a point.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>27</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
